🧠 Auto Command Based on Device Type (Cleaner)

Instead of writing command in inventory, define mapping:

COMMAND_MAP = {
    "juniper": "show configuration | display set | no-more",
    "cisco": "show running-config",
    "fortigate": "show full-configuration",
    "paloalto": "show config running"
}

Then use:

command = COMMAND_MAP.get(device["type"])

